OL,3,CJersey braced for hottest day of the
OL,4,Cyear so far as safety guidance issued
OL,6,FJersey's government has issued
OL,7,Fguidance for how islanders can safely
OL,8,Fenjoy the hottest day of the year so
OL,9,Ffar (29 July).
OL,11,FTemperatures could hit 30C over the
OL,12,Fnext couple of days so islanders are
OL,13,Fbeing warned to take extra precautions
OL,14,Fto stay safe in the heat.
OL,16,FOlder people and children are at
OL,17,Fparticular risk in extreme heat.
