OL,3,CJersey braced for hottest day of the
OL,4,Cyear so far as safety guidance issued
OL,6,F Keep your home cool by closing
OL,7,Fcurtains, opening windows, and using
OL,8,Ffans
OL,10,F Wear a hat and loose light clothing,
OL,11,Ftry to stay in the shade and carry
OL,12,Fwater with you
OL,14,F Wear sun cream when going outside.
